BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/chile38.html

Season: 1938


* NB: for the División de Honor Amateur teams Universidad Catolica and Universidad de Chile, the first round also decided on their possible promotion.  That of Universidad Catolica was rejected after their 2-6 loss, but Universidad de Chile were accepted after reaching a 1-1 draw against Audax Italiano in regulation time (they lost in extra time).



Competition: Chilean Campeonato de Apertura

Round: First Round
; Colo Colo              ; 6-2; Universidad Catolica
; Magallanes                 ; 6-2; Unión Española
; Audax Italiano                 ; 2-1 (aet); Universidad de Chile
; Badminton                          ; 5-4; Santiago Morning 

Round: Semifinals
; Colo Colo              ; 2-1; Magallanes                  
; Audax Italiano             ; 2-1; Badminton

Round: Final
; Colo Colo              ; 3-1; Audax Italiano

*Colo Colo are winners of the Campeonato de Apertura

